---
title: Grilled Dill-Garlic Shrimp Salad with Ranch Dressing and DIY Croutons
description: It's family BBQ time, and this dish makes it easy to customize everyone's plates to their taste. Little one doesn't like croutons or tomatoes? No problem, keep them all for yourself. Everyone loves ranch—drizzle it over everything and this dinner will be a hit!

